${\mathrm{{FeC}}}_{2}{\mathrm{O}}_{4} \cdot 2{\mathrm{H}}_{2}\mathrm{O}$ 在水中的溶解度为

$$
\frac{{0.10}\mathrm{\;g}}{{180}\mathrm{\;g} \cdot {\mathrm{{mol}}}^{-1} \times 1{\mathrm{{dm}}}^{3}} = {5.6} \times {10}^{-4}\mathrm{\;{mol}} \cdot {\mathrm{{dm}}}^{-3}
$$

$$
{\mathrm{{FeC}}}_{2}{\mathrm{O}}_{4} \rightleftharpoons {\mathrm{{Fe}}}^{2 + } + {\mathrm{C}}_{2}{\mathrm{O}}_{4}^{2 - }
$$

$$
{K}_{\mathrm{{sp}}}^{ \ominus } = c\left( {\mathrm{{Fe}}}^{2 + }\right) c\left( {{\mathrm{C}}_{2}{\mathrm{O}}_{4}^{2 - }}\right) = {\left( {5.6} \times {10}^{-4}\right) }^{2} = {3.1} \times {10}^{-7}
$$

